title: #127 - Jim Jefferies & ME
description: Comedian Jim Jefferies & I hang out in the Mancave & talk about British Stand-up vs. American Stand-up vs. Austrailian Stand-up, touring, working on Legit, & one of his most epic drug fueled radio apperances on Opie & Anthony.
